{{ 'section-custom-article.css' | asset_url | stylesheet_tag }}

<article class="article-template" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/BlogPosting">
  <div class="page-width">
    <div class="background-image article-banner w-100 mobile" style="background-image: url({{ section.settings.blog_image1 | img_url: 'master' }})">
    </div> 
    <div class="article-info d-flex justify-content-between align-center w-100">
      <div class="author-info d-flex justify-content-between align-center">
        <img src="{{ article.user.image | img_url: '30x' }}">
        <p class="author-name blog-info-font">{{ article.author }}</p>
      </div>
      <div class="article-detail d-flex justify-content-between align-center">
        <p class="created_at blog-info-font">
          <img src="{{ 'Clock.svg' | asset_url }}"> {{ article.published_at | date: format: 'short' }}
        </p>
        <p class="artile-heart blog-info-font"><img src="{{ 'blog_heart.svg' | asset_url }}"> {{ article.heart }} </p>
        <p class="article-comment blog-info-font"><img src="{{ 'Comment.svg' | asset_url }}"> {{ article.comments_count }} </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <h1 class="heading-font-family font-brown">
      {{ section.settings.article_title1 }}<br>
      {%- if section.settings.article_title2 != blank -%}
        <span class="font-choco">{{ section.settings.article_title2 }}</span>
      {%- endif -%}
    </h1>

    <div class="header-introduction">
      {%- if section.settings.intro_title != blank -%}
        <h2 class="text-font-family font-choco mb-36">{{ section.settings.intro_title}}</h2>
      {%- endif -%}
      <div class="text-font-family font-choco">
        <p>The question of whether we choose crystals or if crystals choose us is a topic that has been debated by crystal enthusiasts for years. Some believe that we are drawn to particular crystals based on our unique energy needs, while others argue that the crystals themselves have an innate ability to choose their owners. Regardless of which perspective one takes, there is no denying the powerful connection that can be formed between a person and their crystal. Exploring this connection can deepen our understanding of the role crystals play in our lives and enhance our appreciation for the natural world.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    {%- if section.settings.blog_image1 -%}
      {%- if section.settings.blog_banner_2 != blank -%}
        <div class="two-background-image">
          <div class="background-image bg-1" style="background-image: url({{ section.settings.blog_image1 | img_url: 'master' }})"></div>
          <div class="background-image bg-2" style="background-image: url({{ section.settings.blog_banner_2 | img_url: 'master' }})"></div>
        </div>
      {%- else -%}
        <div class="background-image article-banner desktop" style="background-image: url({{ section.settings.blog_image1 | img_url: 'master' }})"></div>
      {%- endif -%}
    {%- endif -%}
    
    <div class="article-grid">
      <div class="share">
        <ul>
          <li class="text-font-family font-choco">Share</li>
          <li><a href="http://www.twitter.com/share?url=do-we-choose-crystals-or-do-crystals-choose-us"><img src="{{ 'twitter.png' | asset_url }}"></a></li>
          <li><a href="https://www.facebook.com/sharer/sharer.php?u=do-we-choose-crystals-or-do-crystals-choose-us"><img src="{{ 'facebook.png' | asset_url }}"></a></li>
          <li><a href="https://www.instagram.com/?url=do-we-choose-crystals-or-do-crystals-choose-us"><img src="{{ 'instagram.png' | asset_url }}"></a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="articles">
        <div class="row align-center mb-top">
          <div class="col-md-12">
            <p class="text-font-family font-choco">When it comes to attracting love, there are several crystals that are believed to promote emotional healing and healthy relationships. In this article, we will explore some of the best crystals for love and how they can be used to attract love into your life.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="row align-center mb-top">
          <div class="col-md-6">
            <h2 class="mb-24 text-font-family">
              <a href="#" class="font-choco">1/ Rose Quartz</a>
            </h2>
            <p class="text-font-family font-choco mb-18">One of the most well-known crystals for love is rose quartz. This beautiful pink crystal is believed to promote emotional healing, compassion, and unconditional love. By opening the heart chakra and allowing energy to flow freely, rose quartz can help to attract new love into your life, as well as strengthen existing relationships.</p>
            <p class="text-font-family font-choco mb-18">There are several techniques for using rose quartz to attract love, such as carrying it with you, wearing it as jewelry, or placing it in a love corner of your home. You can also meditate with rose quartz by holding it in your hand and visualizing love and positive energy flowing into your life.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="col-md-6">
            <div style="background-image: url({{ section.settings.blog_image2 | img_url: 'master' }})" class="background-image landing"></div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="row align-center mb-top">
          <div class="col-md-6">
            <h2 class="mb-24 text-font-family">
              <a href="#" class="font-choco">2/ Rhodonite</a>
            </h2>
            <p class="text-font-family font-choco">Rhodonite is another crystal that is believed to promote self-love and attract healthy relationships. This beautiful pink and black crystal is associated with the heart chakra and is believed to help release emotional wounds and promote forgiveness.</p>
            <p class="text-font-family font-choco">To use rhodonite for love, you can carry it with you, wear it as jewelry, or meditate with it. By connecting with its energy and setting intentions for love and healing, you can open yourself up to new love and strengthen existing relationships.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="col-md-6">
            <div style="background-image: url({{ section.settings.blog_image3 | img_url: 'master' }})" class="background-image landing"></div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="row align-center mb-top">
          <div class="col-md-6">
            <h2 class="mb-24 text-font-family">
              <a href="#" class="font-choco">3/ Green Aventurine</a>
            </h2>
            <p class="text-font-family font-choco">Green aventurine is a powerful crystal that is associated with abundance and love. This beautiful green crystal is believed to promote positivity, prosperity, and emotional healing. By opening the heart chakra and allowing energy to flow freely, green aventurine can help to attract new love into your life and enhance existing relationships. To use green aventurine for love, you can carry it with you, place it in your love corner or wealth corner of your home, or meditate with it. By connecting with its energy and setting intentions for love and abundance, you can attract positive energy and open yourself up to new opportunities.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="col-md-6">
            <div style="background-image: url({{ section.settings.blog_image4 | img_url: 'master' }})" class="background-image landing"></div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="row align-center mb-24">
          <div class="col-md-6">
            <h2 class="mb-24 text-font-family">
              <a href="#" class="font-choco">Other Crystals for Love</a>
            </h2>
            <p class="text-font-family font-choco">In addition to rose quartz, rhodonite, and green aventurine, there are several other crystals that are believed to attract love and promote healthy relationships. Clear quartz is a powerful amplifier that can enhance the energy of other crystals and help to manifest love and positivity. Garnet is a deep red crystal that is associated with the root chakra and is believed to help release negative patterns and attract love and intimacy. Moonstone is a beautiful, iridescent crystal that is associated with the feminine energy of the moon and is believed to promote emotional healing and enhance intuition.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="col-md-6">
            <div style="background-image: url({{ section.settings.blog_image2 | img_url: 'master' }})" class="background-image landing"></div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="row align-center">
          <div class="col-md-12">
            <p class="text-font-family font-choco">Using crystals for love and emotional healing can be a powerful tool for attracting love and promoting healthy relationships. Crystals such as rose quartz, rhodonite, and green aventurine can help to promote self-love, enhance positive energy, and attract new love into your life. By setting intentions and using these crystals with respect and gratitude, you can harness their powerful energy to enhance your attractiveness and openness to love.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="col-md-6">
            <div style="background-image: url({{ section.settings.blog_image5 | img_url: 'master' }})" class="background-image landing"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
